Ruoth Nyasaye ohero Jakobo gi nyikwaye


1  Ma e wach Ruoth Nyasaye mane omiyo Malaki mondo onyis jo-Israel. 
2  

Ruoth Nyasaye owacho niya, “Aherou.” To usedwoke kupenje ni, “Ere kaka iherowa?” To Ruoth Nyasaye odwoko ni, “Donge Esau gi Jakobo ne gin owete? Kata kamano ahero Jakobo gi nyikwaye. 
3  Esau gi nyikwaye to asin-go. Aseketho piny gode mag Esau, mi aloko obedo thim ma ondiegi dakie.”


4  Ka nyikwa Esau ma jo-Edom owacho ni kata obedo ni miechgi osekethi kamano, to gibiro gerogi kendo, to Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto dwoko niya, “We mondo gigergi, to abiro kethogi kendo, mi ji noluong jogo ni oganda mar kethruok ma Ruoth Nyasaye okechogo nyaka chieng’. 
5  Ubiro neno gigo gi wang’u ka timore, mi unuwach niya, ‘Kara Ruoth Nyasaye nigi teko kata e pinje mamoko ma ok Israel!’ ”

Ruoth Nyasaye okwero jodolo


6  Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto owacho ni jodolo niya, “Wuowi nyaka mi wuon luor, kendo jatich bende nyaka luor ng’at ma otiyone. To an dak umiya duong’, to an wuonu? Koso dak umiya luor, to an ema utiyona? Usejara, to eka upenja ni, ‘Ere kaka wasejari?’ 
7  Usejara kuom chiwo chiemo ma chik ok oyiego e kendona mar misango, to eka upenja ni ere kaka ok usemiya luor! To usejara kuchayo kendona mar misango. 
8  

Uparo ni en gima kare ka ukelo chiayo ma muofu kata mong’ol kata matuo mondo utimnago misango? To ka da bed ni uchiwo chiayo ma kamano ni ruodhu, bende da obedo mamor kodu, koso da orwakou? 
9  Koro sani un jodolo, kapo ni utemo ni ukwayo Nyasaye mondo okonyu, to ok nowinj kwayou, kendo mano en kethou.”


10  Ruoth Nyasaye Manyalo Gik Moko Duto owacho niya, “Da obedo maber ka ng’at achiel kuomu oloro dhorangeye mag laru mar Hekalu, mondo kik umok mach e kendona mar misango kayiem nono. Ok amor kodu, kendo ok nayie misengni muchiwona. 
11  Ji manie tung’ piny koni gi koni miyo nyinga duong’. Giwang’ona ubani mang’ue ng’ar kuonde duto, kendo gichiwona misengni ma ayiego. Giduto gimiyo nyinga duong’. 
12  To uchaya, kuparo ni kendona mar misango en kama odwanyore, ma unyalo chiwoe chiemo moro amora. 
13  Uwacho niya, ‘Mano kaka waol gi gik makamagi!’ Kendo utwenyona umu. To bende uchiwona jamni mokwal kata mong’ol kata matuo mondo otimnago misango. Uparo ni anyalo yie gi chiwo ma kamago? 
14  Okuong’ ng’at ma jawuond ma timona misango gi chiayo modwanyore kamano mondo ochopgo kuong’ruokne, to oweyo chiache maber e kul. An e ruodh ruodhi, kendo ogendini duto oluora!”

